body:
Freakin' love this. It was one of my favorite GuP doujins even before translation.
Now that it's translated, it just got 10 times better.
Art: 10/10
Story:10/10 (Just no-bullshit, straight to the point causal sex)
Dialogue: 100/10
I swear, 97.6% of all hentai has the exact same goddamn dialogue (You know what i'm talking about).
But this has some witty banter, some sass going back and forth between characters, that just doesn't make it HOT, it also puts a smile on me.
"I won't stop or slow down, even if you beg me to stop!"
"You can't threaten me with a good time". Love that.
I coomed half-way... Gonna save the rest for later.
bless to those who hold knowlege of sequels.
The character tags are takeko nogami and kiyomi sugiyama but wouldn't it be more practical and logical to call them by their soul names. They are hardcore Reki-jo afterall.
